Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.37,0:00:24.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Burger Queen  給你買好了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.37,0:00:24.45,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}注： \N 惡搞的漢堡王<Burger King>
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.69,0:00:29.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.41,0:00:32.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒  沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.37,0:00:40.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以告訴我了嗎  這傷是怎麼弄的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.91,0:00:47.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過還真讓人意外
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.91,0:00:50.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為在E潘朵拉研究所沒法醫治
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.98,0:00:53.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然就遣送回了West·Genetics
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.62,0:01:01.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊莉沙白·梅布利是預料到了這點…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.80,0:01:05.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到外面去冷靜一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.61,0:01:09.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,應該不會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.78,0:01:14.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也多虧這樣  才很難得的能和莎緹拉學姐獨處
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.53,0:01:16.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.75,0:01:20.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有些難為情啊  好久都沒這樣獨處過了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.83,0:01:23.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,獨…處…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.60,0:01:26.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.84,0:01:31.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…  沒… 沒什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.23,0:01:32.91,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}3351
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.02,0:01:33.77,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}前往東京的乘客請注意
