Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.13,0:02:04.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,停下  和哉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.58,0:02:05.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.00,0:02:12.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去那裏
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.89,0:02:15.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,12號登機口？
